# AI Adaptive Assessment

**AI Adaptive Assessment** is a web-based platform for conducting adaptive quizzes and assignments. The system adjusts question difficulty dynamically based on the student's performance and provides real-time analytics for teachers.

---

## Features

- Adaptive question difficulty (1 to 5) based on student accuracy.
- Supports multiple subjects: Maths, Physics, Chemistry, and General Knowledge.
- Student-friendly interface with modern UI/UX.
- Teacher dashboard for analytics:
  - Total attempts
  - Accuracy percentage
  - Average time per question
- Lightweight SQLite database for easy setup.

---

## Technologies Used

- Python 3.x
- Flask (Web framework)
- SQLAlchemy (ORM for SQLite)
- HTML/CSS/JS for frontend

---

## Setup Instructions

1. **Clone the repository:**

```bash
git clone https://github.com/username/AI-Adaptive-Assessment.git
cd AI-Adaptive-Assessment



python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # Linux/Mac
venv\Scripts\activate      # Windows



pip install -r requirements.txt

python app.py

http://127.0.0.1:5000/
AI-Adaptive-Assessment/
│
├─ app.py             # Main application file
├─ data.db            # SQLite database (auto-generated)
├─ requirements.txt   # Python dependencies
├─ README.md          # Project documentation
└─ .gitignore         # Ignored files for Git
